Package: IsoPriceR
Type: Package
Title: Insurance pricing using market data (IsoPriceR)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pierre-O Goffard
Maintainer: Pierre-O Goffard <pierre.olivier.goffard@gmail.com>
Description: For a given insurance policy, take rates from the competitors. Retrieve the underlying risk using a parametric approach. Link the pure premium to the commercial one using an isotonic regression model
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: stats, dplyr, ggplot2, zeallot, mvtnorm, R.utils, ks, resample

